1
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,000
Any news on Coach A-You?

2
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,280
He was killed.

3
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,240
What?

4
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,640
How long have you worked here?

5
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,280
About four years.

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,960
Coach A-You was my senior.

7
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,480
I didn't make it into the league before.

8
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,960
So I came here to help out.

9
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:31,120
There are dozens of gyms in Tuo Cheng, at least.

10
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,240
Do you have any competitors?

11
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,800
I wouldn't call it competition.

12
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,840
After all, the kids here...

13
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,080
...most can't afford tuition.

14
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,200
So, among these kids...

15
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,520
...how many can make it to professional matches?

16
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,520
Not many in the past.

17
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,440
But now there are more.

18
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,200
Because Coach A-You...

19
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,240
...improved the training system.

20
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,320
Most of the kids...

21
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,680
...can go to Ruilin to fulfill their dreams.

22
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,600
Do you have the student roster and match records?

23
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,480
Yes.

24
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:02,520
Over here.

25
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,120
Hello.

26
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,520
Can I ask you some questions?

27
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,960
Training is so tough,

28
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,160
and it's easy to get injured.

29
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,880
Why do you keep at it?

30
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:32,040
At first, I just wanted extra income.

31
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,520
To help support my family.

32
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,680
And save up for tuition.

33
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,080
So, for one fight...

34
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,760
...how much can you earn?

35
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,400
I get about 800 for a fight.

36
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,960
But if I can make the opponent bleed...

37
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,160
...I can get up to two thousand.

38
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,400
So, is Coach A-You...

39
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,960
...usually strict with you?

40
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,320
Here it comes!

41
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,160
The coach is good to everyone.

42
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,360
The gym feels like home.

43
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,000
Eat up, eat up.

44
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,440
Here.

45
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,520
Here, eat more.

46
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,160
Here.

47
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:03,920
Thank you.

48
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,520
For you.

49
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:04,960
Me too.

50
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,200
Give me yours. Here.

51
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,720
My turn, my turn.

52
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,720
I'll give you some extra meat.

53
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,200
Is that enough?

54
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:10,560
Eat plenty.

55
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,160
Add some meat.

56
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,280
Here, Lulu.

57
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,640
Give it to me.

58
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:14,480
Here.

59
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,480
Lulu.

60
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,280
Lulu.

61
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,240
Watch her eyes when you fight.

62
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,560
The most important thing for a fighter is belief.

63
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,920
You can definitely beat her.

64
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,560
Come on! Come on! Come on!

65
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,600
Come on! Come on!

66
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,280
Fighter in black, Lulu.

67
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,120
From A-You Muay Thai Gym.

68
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,880
Fighter in red, Lina.

69
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,440
From Royal Gym.

70
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,800
Fight!

71
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:48,760
Come on!

72
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,600
Punch! Punch!

73
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,360
Come on!

74
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,840
He said he'd send us all to Ruilin.

75
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,760
To stand in the top arena.

76
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,560
You won that match.

77
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,280
But...

78
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,160
...after going through that match...

79
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,920
...I really fell in love with fighting.

80
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,040
I hope that one day...

81
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,160
...girls can also...

82
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,600
...flip into the ring over the ropes.

83
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,720
Do you give the prize money to the coach?

84
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:32,160
Other gyms seem to require giving it to the coach.

85
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:35,160
But Coach A-You never took ours.

86
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:40,960
Shen Man.

87
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,160
What is your name?

88
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,080
Lulu.

89
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,880
Lulu.

90
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,520
Keep it up.

91
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,320
Be careful not to get hurt.

92
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,200
I'm leaving now.

93
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,080
We use public opinion

94
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,760
to break people's feudal superstitions.

95
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,040
But this killer...

96
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,600
uses public opinion to exaggerate supernatural myths.

97
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:16,920
A real pro.

98
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,120
This has become such a big deal.

99
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,640
We must solve the case ASAP.

100
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,720
Chief.

101
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,280
Um...

102
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,520
Did the Director scold you again?

103
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,880
I haven't even scolded you yet.

104
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,160
Chief.

105
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,440
This was sent by the welfare home.

106
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,840
What is it?

107
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,360
I'm starting to understand Jiang Li's

108
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,760
intention in having Shen Man make that video.

109
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,880
Seeing those protesters during the day,

110
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:58,160
their guard up and distrust of us...

111
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,160
I was wondering,

112
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,400
why exactly

113
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,960
did we put on this uniform in the first place?

114
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:10,960
Chief.

115
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,400
I'll go monitor Lin Wan.

116
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,280
I'll go too.

117
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,400
Watch out for that puddle.

118
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,640
Wait a minute.

119
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,600
Among these students' names,

120
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,960
none of the initials have an "L".

121
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,160
Lulu's name has an "L".

122
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,960
But she's so young,

123
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,400
and she admires You Kundee so much.

124
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,200
Do you think it could be

125
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,280
that there are other boxers at the gym

126
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,600
who didn't make it to the pro leagues,

127
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:52,400
and hold a grudge against You Kundee?

128
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,640
We can't rule out that possibility.

129
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,600
But I feel like this matter

130
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,440
isn't that simple.

131
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,960
The previous victims had all done bad things.

132
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,840
Maybe we can start by looking into

133
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,160
what bad things You Kundee

134
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,040
might have actually done.

135
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,920
That way we can identify who made the wish.

136
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,760
Maybe we can find

137
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,600
the connection between the wisher and the killer.

138
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,640
But this You Kundee...

139
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,720
what bad things did he actually do?

140
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,440
He stays at the gym all day.

141
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,760
We can start investigating the gym.

142
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,080
Because Coach A-You

143
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,160
upgraded the training system,

144
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,160
most of the children

145
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,480
can go to Ruilin to fulfill their dreams.

146
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,200
I'm not an expert on boxing,

147
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:34,080
but looking at those kids in the gym,

148
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,720
most of their physical conditions

149
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,160
wouldn't be considered talented.

150
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,840
Do you think the problem might lie in

151
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:40,200
the new training methods?

152
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,200
Boxing isn't exactly a novel sport.

153
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,520
In just two or three days,

154
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,160
for untalented students

155
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,280
to improve so much...

156
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,400
it really doesn't make sense.

157
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:52,960
Let's ask those

158
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,400
kids who went to Ruilin to box.

159
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,520
Maybe there will be clues.

160
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,440
Okay.

161
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:00,400
Let's go.

162
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:23,080
That Lin Wan,

163
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,720
she just buys groceries and watches the kid every day.

164
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,760
There's nothing to it.

165
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,840
Did you read Lin Wan's statement?

166
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,800
What about it?

167
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,840
She even remembers what clothes

168
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,280
You Kundee was wearing before he disappeared.

169
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,200
Doesn't that seem deliberate?

170
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,200
Maybe he only has a few outfits.

171
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,320
But she even remembers the color

172
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,480
of the edges of his shoes.

173
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,800
Maybe he only has a few pairs of shoes.

174
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,560
Keep your voice down.

175
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:49,840
Go, go, go.

176
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,200
Here.

177
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,760
I'm going back.

178
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,520
Stay safe.

179
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:16,920
This is...

180
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,200
What happened here?

181
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,960
Just a naughty kid messing around.

182
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,720
Didn't you ever break toys when you were little?

183
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,920
I'd like to see just how long

184
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,080
this Lin Wan can keep up the act.

185
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:43,320
Shen Man.

186
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,840
Jiang Li.

187
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,000
Your wound needs to be treated.

188
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,240
I bought you some medicine.

189
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,600
Thank you.

190
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,320
Can you apply it yourself?

191
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,680
I can handle it myself, don't worry.

192
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,200
Um...

193
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,800
I didn't bring my house keys.

194
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,240
Your neck.

195
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,240
All done.

196
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,920
I was really naughty as a kid.

197
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,800
My sister always helped me.

198
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,520
Bring the bag over here.

199
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:05,000
Your dad is a murderer.

200
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:07,560
You're no good either.

201
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,600
A family of three.

202
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:20,960
Look.

203
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,720
All the unpleasant things...

204
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,640
will eventually pass.

205
00:13:42,680 --> 00:13:43,440
Yeah.

206
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,680
Life is like a wheel.

207
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,720
Rolling forward without stopping.

208
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,200
The good and the bad...

209
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:51,960
will all pass.

210
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,240
Ruilin Police Station replied.

211
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,440
Did they find any info on those fighters?

212
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,720
They said

213
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,560
the fighters from You Kundee Gym

214
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:14,400
never went to Ruilin

215
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,440
to participate in professional matches.

216
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,600
We can't even find their entry and exit records.

217
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,120
How is that possible?

218
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,960
Then where on earth did You Kundee

219
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,720
hide those fighters?

220
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,240
This place...

221
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:12,800
we won't be coming back here.

222
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,400
The fighters sponsored by You Kundee Gym

223
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,480
are mostly orphans.

224
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:37,800
No one reports it even if they go missing.

225
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,560
There are also some from poor families.

226
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:41,640
Those families have more than one child.

227
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,440
Leaving them at the gym

228
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,200
saves them a lot of worry and trouble.

229
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,880
So You Kundee choosing

230
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:49,200
such people as fighters

231
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,600
was for a specific purpose.

232
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:53,840
Considering the Ai Xia and Cheng Hui cases,

233
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,240
I suspect You Kundee

234
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,320
wanted to use these missing fighters

235
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,840
for illegal activities.

236
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,000
The person who made the wish

237
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,360
might be among these fighters.

238
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:08,320
All clues to the murderer are dead ends now.

239
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:11,320
We have to find the person who made the wish first.

240
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:15,200
Isn't there a coach at the gym?

241
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,600
Can he contact the other fighters?

242
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,480
Hello? Chief.

243
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,600
Lin Wan has closed down the gym.

244
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:44,600
Okay.

245
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:46,880
Come here, come here.

246
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:53,840
What's going on?

247
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:55,960
Take photos.

248
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:03,080
Ma Nuo and Mei Dong followed Lin Wan to the gym.

249
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,800
Lin Wan closed the gym.

250
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:15,960
The gym was smashed up like this.

251
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,200
Lin Wan must really hate the gym.

252
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,440
Right after something happened to You Kundee,

253
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,440
Lin Wan closed down the gym.

254
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,600
Coach Xiao Dong's phone is turned off.
